skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: rainy portland
des: Finding something to do during the nine months of rain in Portland is always a challenge. Rainy Portland helps you discover the best rainy day activities. Ask about the part of town that you are interested in and Rainy Portland will identify fun, indoor activities available there.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
